
Overview of noun brightness

The noun brightness has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (11) brightness -- (the location of a visual perception along a continuum from black to white)
2. brightness, cleverness, smartness -- (intelligence as manifested in being quick and witty)
3. luminosity, brightness, brightness level, luminance, luminousness, light -- (the quality of being luminous; emitting or reflecting light; "its luminosity is measured relative to that of our sun")
